title: 191: 2017 Manning Passing Academy
itunes:title: 191: 2017 Manning Passing Academy
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is joined by NFL Network's Rhett Lewis following the 22nd annual Manning Passing Academy to break down the latest crop of college quarterbacks that attended including 2016 Heisman trophy winner Lamar Jackson and potential 2018 1st round selections in Wyoming's Josh Allen and USC's Sam Darnold.
